<main>
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    
    <section class="about-content">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            The CSE 340 Service Network is dedicated to bridging the gap between passionate volunteers 
            and organizations that drive meaningful change. We believe that by providing a centralized 
            platform for service projects, we can foster a stronger, more connected community.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <p>
            We curate and maintain a database of local organizations and service projects, 
            making it easy for individuals to find opportunities that match their skills 
            and interests. From environmental conservation to educational support, our 
            network covers a wide range of impactful categories.
        </p>
    </section>
</main>

